owl:Ontology.terms:title: Real Estate Ontology
owl:Ontology.rdfs:comment: This ontology describes real estate using a controlled vocabulary based on a dataset from a prop-tech company. It is aimed at the german market and models some concepts only valid in Germany (e.g., energy pass).
